text: Ints Dālderis (born 10 February 1971, Jūrmala, Latvian SSR) is a Latvian clarinetist and politician of initially the People's Party, then New Era Party, then Unity and finally Movement For!. He was Minister of Culture of Latvia from March 12, 2009 to November 3, 2010. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:People from Jūrmala Category:People's Party (Latvia) politicians Category:New Era Party politicians Category:New Unity politicians Category:Movement For! politicians Category:Ministers of Culture of Latvia Category:Deputies of the 10th Saeima Category:Deputies of the 12th Saeima Category:Latvian musicians Category:Recipients of the Order of the Cross of Terra Mariana, 1st Class
